.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, water
There are 2 different nationalities: french, colombian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, coral
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
2. the person drinking water is the fan of pop##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the french##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up        | water   |
| Nationality         | colombian | french |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| Color           | coral        | mauve    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

